  "body": "The following program compiles,\r\n\r\n```\r\ncontract C { type T0 is uint; }\r\ncontract D { C.T0 x; }\r\n```\r\n\r\nbut the next one does not.\r\n\r\n```\r\ncontract C { type T0 is uint; }\r\ncontract D { C.T0 x = C.T0.wrap(uint(1)); }\r\n```\r\n\r\nFound by fuzzing.",
